name: cUbe (itch) (Crazy Potato)
description:
cUbe, a fun and difficult dodging obstacles game! Where you must get to the end of the level, but beware of the obstacles that lay before you...

This game was made by me, Crazy Potato, I'm a early game programmer and developer and my main game engine I used is Unity. This game is made for everybody! But it is still a work in progress and is mainly meant for me and my friends to check out but I will be releasing new versions here of it!
